1--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Community</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nClick Add Friend to befriend another adventurer.

2--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Beauty</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nExpress yourself with new hair styles, dyes, and faces.

3--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Taxi</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nOnce you discover a taxi stop, you can ride a taxi there from anywhere.

4--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Auto-loot</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nYou must reach Lv. 10 to use the Auto-loot function.

5--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Mount</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nRun as hard as you can to earn the <FONT color='#FFD200'>A True Marathoner II</FONT> trophy... and get a mount!

6-Fishing-.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Fishing</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nVisit Pesca and complete the <FONT color='#FFD200'>First Touch</FONT> quest to receive a fishing pole. Fill your Fish Album to earn special items.

7--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Kay's Games</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nJoin in Kay's events to earn some serious experience!

8-MeratMarket-.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Meret Market</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nCheck the Meret Market for hot new products.

9--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Safe</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nStore your items and mesos in the vaults found in every town.

10--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Emote</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nClick the button next to the chat window to use all kinds of expressive actions.

11--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Balmy Farm</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nDefeat the pack and protect the herd!

12-GuildSystem01-.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Guild</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nIf you're not in a guild yet, use the Search function to join one.

13-ArcadeSystem-.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Maple Arcade</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nYou can enjoy a wide range of mini-games at the Maple Arcade.

15--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Find Party</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nFind a group of adventurers to play with.

19-MusicInstrument-.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Play Instrument</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nIf you have an instrument and a music score, you can play music! Visit the Royal Music Academy to get started.

20--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Enchantment</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nVisit enchanters to grant your equipment new powers.

21--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Golma Apartments</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nYour help is needed to scold a very bad piggy.

22--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Flying Balloon</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nGet a flying balloon and float effortlessly through the sky.

27--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Dismantle</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nUse the Onyx Extractor with <FONT color='#FFD200'>a Lv. 20 or higher piece of equipment</FONT> to get an Onyx Crystal.

28--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Black Market</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nShop for rare items you can't find anywhere else.

32-ShadowCataclysm-.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Shadow Gate</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nThe Land of Darkness lies beyond the ominous Shadow Gate.

37--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Real Estate</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nIf you own property, you can manage it here. If you don't have any property yet, why not try a starter home in Evansville?

38--.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Assistant</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nHired assistants for your house can craft items for you. Visit Tabatha in Tria to hire assistants for mesos. You can also hire assistants from the Meret Market.

59-KarkarIsland-.name: Lumiwind Airship\n \nThe Lumiwind can take you straight to Karkar Island.

65-AricariDailyQ-.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Daily Quests</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nComplete daily quests in Queenstown and Ludari City to earn mesos and rue.

67-Season3-.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Blue Stars</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nGather blue stars and use them to purchase various items from the Starkeepers.

69-ShadowCrack-.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Twisted Pocket Realm</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nFace the forces of evil head-on deep within the Land of Darkness.

71-ItemSocketSystem-.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Gemstones</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nEquip gemstones to power up your equipment.

242-JobChange_01-.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Job Rank</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nAfter reaching level 60, you can begin a quest to increase your job rank.

243-Lapenshard01-.name: <FONT color='#FFD200' size='15'>Lapenshards</FONT>\n<FONT size='3'> </FONT>\nAfter completing your job rank quest, speak with Lanemone at the Frontier Foundation. After completing her quests, you'll be able to harness the awesome power of lapenshards.
